 Bravour.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 25. Feb 2021) 7aMEDICAL / Nursing / General.2bisacsh  aAltenhilfe.  aMDK.  aQPR.  aQualitätsmanagement.  aQualitätsprüfungsrichtlinie.1 aRichter, Ronald, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aRichter, Ronald, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWipp, Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978374860191340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783748601913423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783748601913.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles